solution.p:
To find the recursive equation, we need to solve for u_{n+1}.
u_{n+1}-u_n = 1.4 u_n - \frac{3}{u_n} u_{n+1} = 2.4 u_n - \frac{3}{u_n}
This recursive equation gives us a map from a current value u_n to the next value u_{n+1} in the sequence, u_n \mapsto u_{n+1}, which is the projection function u_{n+1} = f(u_n) = 2.4 u_n - \frac{3}{u_n}. This means that using an input x gives f(x) = 2.4 x - \frac{3}{x}.
